results.description:
This collection of files can also be found in my shop as individual designs. Please go to my main shop page and type in LL010 in the search box and all designs in this collection will come up.

**Now includes EPS format files! If using Design Space/Cricut software, please use the SVG file labeled "Cricut". My files do NOT work with Cricut Craft Room. If using Silhouette Studio basic, please use the DXF file. If using Studio DE, please use the SVG file.

PLEASE READ AND UNDERSTAND BEFORE PURCHASING
Thank you for visiting my digital design shop. Please understand that you are purchasing a digital design ONLY. You are not purchasing any finished product using this design and no physical item(s) will be sent to you. I do not have knowledge of every cutting and graphics software on the market so please know how to use these files BEFORE you purchase. I am glad to help you with simple questions if I am able to do so. If you find a problem with the file itself that needs to be addressed by me, please send me a convo and I will look into the matter and fix it as needed. Most of my files are distributed in a zipped file folder and will need to be unzipped by you in order to access the enclosed files. Files are available for instant download as soon as you complete the purchase in most cases. You can find your purchased files by clicking on the “you” at the top of the Etsy page and then on “purchases and reviews”. Simply locate your purchase and then click on the blue download button. Please make a note of where the file is being stored on your computer when downloading because I can’t help you with locating the files once downloaded.

My files are provided to you in the following formats:
►JPG // (printable image with either a white or gray background-image will blur when increased to sizes over 6”x 6”)
►PNG // (a printable image with no background-can be used with a background of your choosing-image will blur when increased to sizes over 6”x 6”))
►AI // (Adobe Illustrator format for use with Adobe Illustrator and some cutting software platforms)
►EPS (works with many higher end cutters as well as Illustrator and other design software)
►SVG // (scalable vector graphics can be enlarged with no distortion or pixilation and can be used with many cutting software platforms) SVG files are grouped together by color as shown in the photo
►SVG Cricut Version //This version works with Cricut Design Space and is completely ungrouped for you so that you can cut however you wish in as many colors as you wish.
►DXF // (this format can be used in the basic Silhouette cutting software)

SMALL BUSINESS and PERSONAL USE
All of my files may be used for small business and personal use with the following agreement
-files may be used for personal use (no selling of the end product) or for small business use (making and selling finished items) with NO restrictions on how many finished items you make
-Finished items include decals, printed invitations, tiles, tumblers, t-shirts, etc. where you use the file to make an end product
-Digital Files may NOT be distributed or sold in whole or in part in ANY digital format and may not be resold as a digital file, as clip art or as part of a digital paper design, distributed in any digital format on the world wide web such as Facebook, Pinterest, Tumbler, Instagram, Forums, etc.
-When generating “mock-up” photos for your business using the .jpg or .png format, watermarks (of your business name) should be placed over the image to prevent vectorizing of the image
-I do NOT allow “tracing” or otherwise vectorizing my designs for ANY reason! Please respect this!

REFUNDS
Because of the digital nature of my shop, I do not offer refunds for ANY reason for any design in my shop. If you have questions that need to be answered, please ask them BEFORE you purchase the file. Please understand this BEFORE YOU PURCHASE.

EMBROIDERY CONVERSION
If you desire to convert my files into an embroidery file for your own personal to be used on items given away or kept by you (no selling of the resulting digital file), then no additional license is necessary. If you wish to convert the file for resale of the resulting digital embroidery file, then you will need to purchase my commercial embroidery license found here...

https://www.etsy.com/listing/169876239/commercial-embroidery-license-agreement?ref=shop_home_active_1&ga_search_query=COMMERCIAL

When purchasing the commercial embroidery license, please note that the license only applies to a SINGLE design. If you are purchasing a collection, you will need to purchase a license for each design you wish to convert and sell.

COPYRIGHT
All digital files in this Etsy shop are created and owned by Lyrical Letters Design and may not be sold or redistributed in any digital format. This copyright will be enforced as necessary. Thank you for respecting this copyright and the integrity of my shop.
